#### End

~~~ .coda-sample.php
->end($unit = null, $dent = null);
~~~

Close the opened `<title>` tag:

~~~ .php
echo $union->end('title');
~~~

~~~ .php
echo $union->end('title', 0);
~~~

Result:

~~~ .php
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <title>
      test title
    </title>
~~~

~~~ .php
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <title>
      test title
</title>
~~~

Close all of the opened tags:

~~~ .php
echo $union->end(true);
~~~

Result:

~~~ .php
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <title>
      test title
    </title>
  </head>
</html>
~~~

Close with broken tag:

~~~ .php
echo $union->end('foo');
~~~

Result:

~~~ .php
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <title>
      test title
    </foo>
~~~

